org.apache.drill.exec.store.mapr.db

Class RestrictedMapRDBSubScanSpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.exec.store.mapr.db.MapRDBSubScanSpec
      • org.apache.drill.exec.store.mapr.db.RestrictedMapRDBSubScanSpec
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<MapRDBSubScanSpec>

    public class RestrictedMapRDBSubScanSpec
extends MapRDBSubScanSpec
    A RestrictedMapRDBSubScanSpec encapsulates a join instance which contains the ValueVectors of row keys and is associated with this sub-scan and also exposes an iterator type interface over the row key vectors.

        public int hasRowKeys(int numRowKeysToRead)
        Returns number of rowKeys that can be read. Number of rowKeys returned will be numRowKeysToRead at the most i.e. it will be less than numRowKeysToRead if only that many exist in the currentBatch.
